name: results-of-mercury-injection-capillary-pressure-tests-on-outcrop-samples-in-the-tyonek-area-of-
notes: This data set conveys information about samples collected during fieldwork in the Tyonek area of Cook Inlet. Samples were collected from outcrops for Mercury Injection Capillary Pressure (MICP) analyses.
